the opportunity for all

00:15:52.536 --> 00:15:55.876
and actually being able
to gather information

00:15:55.876 --> 00:15:59.106
across a broad spectrum of
media that will allow you

00:15:59.106 --> 00:16:01.566
to fashion your understanding
of a world.

